  KEY FLOWS
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

  AUTH FLOW
  ─────────
  Browser ──POST /auth/login──► Spring Boot ──bcrypt.compare──► MongoDB
         ◄── httpOnly cookies ──                                (users)
              access_token (15min)
              refresh_token (7 days)

  TOKEN REFRESH (silent, handled by Axios interceptor)
  ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Browser ──any API call──► 401 ──► POST /auth/refresh ──► validate refresh_token
         ◄── new access_token cookie ──────────────────────── in MongoDB
         ──► retry original request

  ADD TO CART + REAL-TIME INVENTORY
  ──────────────────────────────────
  Browser ──POST /cart/add──► CartService ──check stock──► MongoDB (products)
                                         ──save cart──► MongoDB (carts)
                                         ──publish──► WebSocket /topic/inventory/{id}
         ◄── all subscribers update stock badge in real-time

  CHECKOUT + PAYMENT
  ──────────────────
  Browser ──POST /orders/place──► create Order (PENDING) ──► MongoDB (orders)
          ──simulate payment (2s delay)──
          ──POST /orders/payment/confirm──► set PAID/FAILED
                                        ──► deduct stock in MongoDB
                                        ──► publish WS inventory events
                                        ──► clearCart in MongoDB
          ◄── fetchCart() called ──► cart badge resets to 0
          ──► show confirmation screen (SUCCESS ✅ / FAIL ❌)